    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194340/extras/a4e3a912f300a65ac6a53fcfa8c08a59.avif?t=1768768981\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>We Are Alive</strong> 是一款合作恐怖游戏，由一名独立开发者制作，并得到了挚友的帮助。游戏支持至少1名玩家，最多可4人一起游玩。你将扮演一名侦探，任务是调查古老精神病院病人神秘失踪的案件，并揭开真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194340/extras/c05664408260c50b532e51616be065df.poster.avif?t=1768768981\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194340/extras/c05664408260c50b532e51616be065df.webm?t=1768768981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194340/extras/c05664408260c50b532e51616be065df.mp4?t=1768768981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>调查 </strong>你需要找到并收集分散在医院各处的证据、钥匙和弹药。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>惊吓(突发惊吓) </strong>游戏中有大量不同的突发惊吓，时刻让你保持警惕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的鬼魂 </strong>游戏中有多个鬼魂，每个鬼魂都有自己独特的性格和特征。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索 </strong>随着你深入探索，沿途的主题也会随之变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>谜题 </strong>在你的旅途中，你会遇到各种各样的谜题，解开它们可以解锁新的道路，推动你继续前进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194340/extras/d0ede6f7282e3cc4b70a7580e27d6ca1.poster.avif?t=1768768981\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194340/extras/d0ede6f7282e3cc4b70a7580e27d6ca1.webm?t=1768768981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194340/extras/d0ede6f7282e3cc4b70a7580e27d6ca1.mp4?t=1768768981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装备 </strong>你始终配备手电筒和手枪。不过，你的弹药可能会耗尽，这会带来一些小麻烦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多人游戏 </strong>你可以单人游戏或与多达4名玩家一起游戏。如果你更喜欢和朋友一起玩，可能会更有趣。但游戏并不会因此变得更容易，因为你仍然需要沟通、分享弹药，并作为一个团队找到前进的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可重玩性 </strong>鬼魂（AI）、物品和道具的生成都是随机的，确保你每次游戏的体验都独一无二。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的旅程中，你会遇到各种鬼魂、突发惊吓、恐怖音效等。所有这些都经过精心设计，以优化你的体验，同时采用简洁的用户界面，让你全身心投入到游戏中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194340/extras/091c430df2f8a38573f6c2d1e1f4cbb3.poster.avif?t=1768768981\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194340/extras/091c430df2f8a38573f6c2d1e1f4cbb3.webm?t=1768768981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194340/extras/091c430df2f8a38573f6c2d1e1f4cbb3.mp4?t=1768768981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>警告 </strong>极少数人在接触某些视觉图像时，可能会出现癫痫发作的情况，包括视频游戏中可能出现的闪光灯或图案。即使没有癫痫或癫痫发作史的人，也可能因未被诊断的疾病而在玩视频游戏时出现这种“光敏性癫痫发作”。如果你出现任何症状，请立即停止游戏并咨询医生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
